The '''[[2015 in Brazilian football|2015 season]]''' is '''[[Gr<U+00EA>mio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense]]''''s 112th season in existence and the club's [[Campeonato Brasileiro S<U+00E9>rie A|10th consecutive season]] in the top flight of [[Football in Brazil|Brazilian football]]. To this season, Gr<U+00EA>mio remained [[Luiz Felipe Scolari]] as their [[Head coach|manager]]. The club signed with [[Umbro]] as a new supplier of sports equipment.

