===Kit===
Supplier: [[Umbro]]<br>
Sponsor(s): [[Banrisul]] / [[Telecom Italia Mobile|TIM]] / [[UNIMED|Unimed]] / Tramontina

This is the first season that [[Umbro]] supplies kits for [[Gr<U+00EA>mio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense|Gr<U+00EA>mio]], after three years of partnership with [[Topper (sports)|Topper]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Fechado com Umbro para 2015, Gr<U+00EA>mio j<U+00E1> recebeu R$ 10 mi da nova fornecedora|url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/blogs/especial-blog/dinheiro-em-jogo/post/fechado-com-umbro-para-2015-gremio-ja-recebeu-r-10-mi-da-nova-fornecedora.html|publisher=Globo Esporte}}</ref>

